@JwtAuthApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5158
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Register a new user
POST {{JwtAuthApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo",
  "email": "demo@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST {{JwtAuthApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get weather forecast (protected - requires JWT)
GET {{JwtAuthApi_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
